snippet.title: Best VGM 2371 - Castlevania : Dawn of Sorrow - Pitch Black Intrusion (Lost Village)
snippet.description:

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Castlevania: Dawn of Sorrow (2005)
Pitch Black Intrusion (Lost Village)
Michiru Yamane
